WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.631
after criticizing

00:00:00.632 --> 00:00:02.139
the organization of the world cup

00:00:02.140 --> 00:00:02.940
by the qatar

00:00:03.051 --> 00:00:04.909
including on the fate of migrant workers

00:00:04.910 --> 00:00:06.594
who have died by the thousands on the construction sites

00:00:07.211 --> 00:00:08.250
now France is

00:00:08.251 --> 00:00:08.719
she too

00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:10.699
in the face of a controversy over the organization of the jo

00:00:10.700 --> 00:00:11.908
deux-mille-vingt-quatre

00:00:12.080 --> 00:00:14.433
liberation met with undocumented workers

00:00:14.434 --> 00:00:17.228
who are employed by a subcontractor company

00:00:17.312 --> 00:00:18.031
who works

00:00:18.032 --> 00:00:20.135
on the construction sites of the jodeux-mille-vingt-quatre

00:00:20.248 --> 00:00:22.159
among them there are handlers

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:23.796
in charge of carrying bags of cement

00:00:23.928 --> 00:00:26.356
of more than ten kilos on thirteen floors

00:00:26.608 --> 00:00:27.731
there are branchers

00:00:27.732 --> 00:00:29.832
specialized in reinforced concrete construction

00:00:30.208 --> 00:00:32.469
then there are men who do everything and pick up the earth

00:00:32.470 --> 00:00:33.472
build the walls

00:00:33.488 --> 00:00:34.336
make masonry

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:36.579
all for a little over eighty euros

00:00:36.580 --> 00:00:37.757
not reported per day

00:00:38.162 --> 00:00:40.397
regardless of weather conditions and one hundred days off

00:00:40.722 --> 00:00:43.437
the workers are outraged they have no right

00:00:43.802 --> 00:00:44.738
no site maintenance

00:00:44.962 --> 00:00:45.898
no safety shoes

00:00:46.362 --> 00:00:47.837
we don't pay for their navigago pass

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:50.574
have no medical examination and not even signed a contract

00:00:50.967 --> 00:00:52.412
they get sick or hurt

00:00:52.487 --> 00:00:54.016
the boss replaces them the next day

00:00:54.645 --> 00:00:56.916
one of the workers even stated that on the site

00:00:57.007 --> 00:00:58.470
there are almost only foreigners

00:00:58.471 --> 00:01:00.056
Pakistani for electricity

00:01:00.287 --> 00:01:01.496
Arabs for plumbing

00:01:01.967 --> 00:01:03.216
endorsements for masonry

00:01:03.567 --> 00:01:04.592
what do you think all this

00:01:04.665 --> 00:01:05.994
give us your opinion in comments
